## Netlify + Supabase Branch Wiring

```bash
# netlify.toml
[build]
  command = "npm run build"
  publish = ".next"

# Branch deploys automatically use Supabase branch credentials
# Netlify integration (Dashboard → Integrations → Netlify) handles this:
#   - PR deploy → branch DB credentials injected as env vars
#   - Production deploy → production DB credentials
# No manual env var management needed when integration is enabled
```

```
Setup:
Dashboard → Project Settings → Integrations → Netlify → Connect site
→ Supabase automatically injects SUPABASE_URL and SUPABASE_ANON_KEY
  (or new key names) into each Netlify deploy context
```

