## Branch Types

| Type | Lifecycle | Use for |
|---|---|---|
| Ephemeral | Created on PR open, deleted on PR close | Feature branches, bug fixes |
| Persistent | Never deleted automatically | Staging environment |

```bash
# Create a persistent staging branch
supabase branches create --name staging --persistent

# Point your staging Netlify site to this branch
# Dashboard → Branching → staging → copy API URL and keys
```
